{"title":"山水天地间——民航之歌","authors":["韩志国"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山水天地间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——民航之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩志国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山恋着水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水环着山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代一代的好儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔在山水间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝携彩霞晨风去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜伴星光明月还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开花又落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月缺月又圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脸微笑一身汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来永恒的春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放一只只银鸽飞向遥远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留一串串故事讲给明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天连着地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地接着天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年一年的好时光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流淌在天地间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端杯冷饮送温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧碗热茶洗风寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云聚云又散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路近路又远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔热情一身胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱写多彩的诗篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒一片片深情回赠大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱一支支心曲献给蓝天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}